---
---
<section id="register" class="v3-reg">
  <div class="v3-reg-inner">

    <div class="v3-reg-left" data-v3-reveal="right">
      <p class="v3-reg-marker">—06—</p>
      <h2 class="v3-reg-heading">Be first on the horizon.</h2>
      <p class="v3-reg-body">We are opening in 2026. Before we publish rates or take bookings through any platform, we will write to everyone on this list directly — with dates, prices, and first right of refusal on the rooms that are hardest to get.</p>
      <p class="v3-reg-body">We do not sell your details. We do not send newsletters. You will hear from us when there is something worth saying.</p>
      <blockquote class="v3-reg-quote">« One conviction. One cliff. One sea. »</blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="v3-reg-right" data-v3-reveal="left" data-v3-delay="80">
      <form class="v3-reg-form" name="v3-register" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
        <p style="display:none"><label>Leave empty: <input name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" /></label></p>

        <div class="v3-reg-field">
          <label class="v3-reg-label" for="v3-name">Full name *</label>
          <input class="v3-reg-input" id="v3-name" type="text" name="name" required autocomplete="name" placeholder="Your name" />
        </div>

        <div class="v3-reg-field">
          <label class="v3-reg-label" for="v3-email">Email address *</label>
          <input class="v3-reg-input" id="v3-email" type="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" placeholder="your@email.com" />
        </div>

        <div class="v3-reg-field">
          <label class="v3-reg-label" for="v3-country">Country of residence</label>
          <input class="v3-reg-input" id="v3-country" type="text" name="country" autocomplete="country-name" placeholder="Where are you writing from?" />
        </div>

        <div class="v3-reg-field">
          <label class="v3-reg-label" for="v3-source">How did you find Green Horizon?</label>
          <select class="v3-reg-input v3-reg-select" id="v3-source" name="source">
            <option value="" disabled selected>Word of mouth, press, social…</option>
            <option value="word-of-mouth">Word of mouth</option>
            <option value="press">Press</option>
            <option value="social-media">Social media</option>
            <option value="other">Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="v3-reg-field">
          <label class="v3-reg-label" for="v3-msg">Anything you would like to say</label>
          <textarea class="v3-reg-input v3-reg-textarea" id="v3-msg" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Questions, preferred dates, room preferences…"></textarea>
        </div>

        <p class="v3-reg-privacy">Your details are held securely and used only to contact you about Green Horizon. We do not share or sell your data. Fields marked * are required.</p>

        <button class="v3-reg-submit" type="submit">Register interest</button>
      </form>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
